{"CEIL":[{"def":"To overlay or cover the inner side of the roof of; to furnish with a ceiling; as, to ceil a room.","pos":""},{"def":"To line or finish a surface, as of a wall, with plaster, stucco, thin boards, or the like.","pos":""}],"CEILING":[{"def":"The inner planking of a vessel.","pos":""}],"CEINTURE":[{"def":"A cincture, girdle, or belt; -- chiefly used in English as a dressmaking term.","pos":""}]}